    "title": {
        "rendered": "MatR: Bruce Springsteen and Ringo Starr and His All Starr Band, Photograph"
    },
    "content": {
        "rendered": "<p>In 1989, with no E Street Band tour on the horizon, Clarence and Nils joined the original incarnation of Ringo Starr&#8217;s All-Star Band (which also included Levon Helm, Joe Walsh, Dr. John, Billy Preston, and other great artists).</p>\n<p>When the tour came around to the Garden State Arts Center, Bruce joined his bandmates on-stage during the encores for four songs, including Ringo&#8217;s hit, &#8220;Photograph.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/EzxoTbt0FRU?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p>This was the only time Bruce is known to have performed &#8220;Photograph.&#8221; Two months later, Bruce re-connected with Clarence and Nils during Starr&#8217;s Japanese tour leg&#8211;this time by phone, to break the news that he was ending the E Street Band.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/nevdSt_2PIM?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>Photograph</strong><br />\n<strong>First performed:</strong> August 11, 1989 (Holmdel, NJ)<br />\n<strong>Last performed:</strong> August 11, 1989 (Holmdel, NJ)</p>\n",
        "protected": false
    },
    "excerpt": {
        "rendered": "<p>One time only: Bruce guests with Ringo Starr and His All-Starr Band for Ringo&#8217;s classic &#8220;Photograph.&#8221;</p>\n",
        "protected": false
    },
